      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor; default acceptance applies.",
      "rationale": "At Model Risk Level 2, explicit iterative convergence error quantification beyond residual monitoring is not required. Residuals converged to 1e-5 for all equations; no further assessment is mandated."
    },
    {
