    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 with documented justification. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in CPB applications at the stated operating envelope.",
